<title>Vawn - tuoidawng</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Sietlei hingmi zatam suilung damna dingin,
 Min lun Chung Pathien in vawn tuoidawng ei chawihsak;
 Tuni hin ken le ka pawm hi ka etchim loh,
 Chung Pathien in veng hen A vanglim nuoi ahin.

[V2]
 U leh nau in kipakin ei lawppih chiet un,
 Kipahna chul theilo go thil bang ei piek hi;
 Paktil bangin chawi hitiu nausen deihum hi,
 A dam kumkhuo sawt hen a vanglim nuoi ahin.

[V3]
 2. A chun leh zuo'n kumsawta ka lungtup pen uh,
 Thimthu leh laigilah siktui in um mahleh;
 Chung Pathien venna leh thahatna zalzo in,
 Anglai a pawmin vawnsen sakmel I mu tai.

[V4]
 3. Lawp chim puong ie vawnsen tuoi til dawng lai cha hi,
 Chung Pathien leh a chun leh zuo suihlung tuok di'n;
 Chang bang damin laituol nga bangin leng hen la,
 Suihlung pilin a hinkhuo gui bangin sau hen.

[V5]
 4. Malsawmna lien, vangphatna lien thilthawnpiek hi,
 Nausen deihum laigila pieng vawntuoidawng hi,
 Gentheia alang vailo dingin sietlei ah,
 Chung Pathien in khawtuoh zing ta hen la, Amen</lyrics>
</song>